00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:25,100
 Where am I? 

23
00:02:26,234 --> 00:02:28,088
 Where is everyone? 

24
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:54,700
 After coming back from the Time Rift, I haven't been able to rest well. 

25
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:34,500
Jinzhao! You finally woke up.

26
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:37,000
Wait for me. Stay here, don't move.

27
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:47,300
Jinzhao, I made noodles with eggs for you.

28
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:49,200
Have some.

29
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,700
 Only when I grow up can I become stronger 

30
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:01,500
 and protect those I want to protect. 

31
00:04:01,500 --> 00:04:05,400
 Jinzhao, I want to protect you in the future too. 

32
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,600
How is it?

33
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:35,400
It's all right.

34
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:39,400
Just all right?

35
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:47,900
Actually, you've grasped some essence of the noodles.

36
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:56,500
I've decided to give our noodles a name!

37
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:01,300
Let's call it Yue's Egg Noodles!

38
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:03,000
Sound good?

39
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,200
Jinzhao,

40
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:10,500
you're terrible at picking names,

41
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:13,200
just like the noodles you make.

42
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:16,200
It's been three years already.

43
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:20,000
In your noodles, there are always just two greens and one egg.

44
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,900
What, what, what?

45
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,200
Have a problem with it?

46
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,800
Yes, I'm telling the absolute truth.

47
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:29,000
You can't tell the absolute truth, only the partial truth.

48
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,500
Third Brother! Third Brother!

49
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,400
Why are you here?

50
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:39,300
Third Brother, didn't you promise to make me a grass dragonfly?

51
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:41,500
When will you do it?

52
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,400
 Why does it feel odd? 

53
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:46,200
 It feels like I'm living someone else's life. 

54
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:48,200
 But Qi feels so familiar. 

55
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,800
Third Brother?

56
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:54,000
Come. I'll make you one.

57
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:04,200
Why do you always cling to my third brother?

58
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:07,500
Children should have manners. Call me "sister".

59
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,200
No, I already have a sister.

60
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:14,500
Really? If you call me sister, I can make noodles for you.

61
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,800
You're so annoying.

62
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:26,500
Third Brother, have you finished?

63
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:28,100
Almost.

64
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,500
Done.

65
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:35,700
Third Brother, is this a dragonfly?

66
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:37,600
You used to do it so well.

67
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:40,600
Why is it so ugly now?

68
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,100
That's right.

69
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:46,500
Your brother has never been good at drawing or braiding straw.

70
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:48,400
 That's not true. 

71
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:57,800
I mean, I can draw. But I don't braid things that well.

72
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:00,300
I made one though, didn't I?

73
00:07:00,300 --> 00:07:04,000
You doubt it? I'll get the ones he made before.

74
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:11,800
You're good at drawing?

75
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,700
Of course.

76
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,700
Let's go for a walk.

77
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:20,300
Okay.

78
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:30,400
Why didn't he wait for me like he used to?

79
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:59,400
Everyone says that Yujie Hub is my home,

80
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:03,400
but this place seems so strange to me.

81
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:06,800
The only familiar thing is you.

82
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:12,950
Shifang, Xian Qing, Zhaoyan, and Ming Xiu.

83
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:15,000
These few friends.

84
00:08:23,434 --> 00:08:25,034
Me too.

85
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,500
I don't know why.

86
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:30,200
After returning from Guixu,

87
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:35,200
I seem to have a new understanding about myself being a weapon.

88
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:38,900
Everyone has things beyond their control.

89
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:41,500
I'm not the only one suffering.

90
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:47,200
If Zhu Yu loses control, the entire realm will be plunged into misery.

91
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:52,000
I think I'm doing the right thing by stopping her.

92
00:09:31,814 --> 00:09:33,455
Sit.

93
00:09:41,861 --> 00:09:44,301
Let's clear things up first.

94
00:09:44,302 --> 00:09:47,301
First, in the past three years,

95
00:09:47,301 --> 00:09:50,002
Hengdao Sect has been an enemy to me.

96
00:09:50,002 --> 00:09:54,182
If you want me to do something, please clarify it first.

97
00:09:54,182 --> 00:09:57,882
If I agree, I can do it for you.

98
00:10:11,861 --> 00:10:16,402
I know you all have deep connections with the Righteous Martial Alliance.

99
00:10:16,402 --> 00:10:19,541
I want you to represent the Hengdao Sect

100
00:10:19,541 --> 00:10:23,202
and propose a collaboration with Zuo Guanren.

101
00:10:23,202 --> 00:10:25,581
Together, we can fight against Zhu Yu.

102
00:10:27,702 --> 00:10:29,441
Zhu Yu is in the sky.

103
00:10:29,441 --> 00:10:31,902
What can Zuo Guanren do?

104
00:10:34,381 --> 00:10:39,401
I've already given her the fake Rehai key ring.

105
00:10:39,401 --> 00:10:42,162
Zhu Yu has long coveted the power of Rehai.

106
00:10:42,162 --> 00:10:45,062
She will surely bring the Yu Clan to Earth.

107
00:10:45,062 --> 00:10:47,302
At that time, the Righteous Martial Alliance will restrain the Yu Clan,

108
00:10:47,302 --> 00:10:49,861
while we unbind Mist Soul and Zhu Yu.

109
00:10:49,861 --> 00:10:52,182
Will Zhu Yu buy it?

110
00:10:53,621 --> 00:10:56,021
She doesn't know the key ring is fake.

111
00:10:56,021 --> 00:10:58,082
When she tries to open Rehai,

112
00:10:58,082 --> 00:11:03,962
as long as Luo Zhaoyan can secretly use the real key ring to help her,

113
00:11:03,962 --> 00:11:08,302
she'll absorb the power of Rehai

114
00:11:08,302 --> 00:11:13,541
and provoke Mist Soul to initiate the spell for unbinding.

115
00:11:14,582 --> 00:11:16,781
After Zhu Yu loses the power of Mist Soul,

116
00:11:16,781 --> 00:11:19,702
her transformation will continue and put her in agony.

117
00:11:19,702 --> 00:11:24,202
She'll naturally return to Mist Soul to suppress her transformation.

118
00:11:24,202 --> 00:11:26,901
That's when she'll be at her weakest,

119
00:11:26,901 --> 00:11:30,361
and the best time for you two to kill her.

120
00:11:30,361 --> 00:11:35,701
At that time, we'll bombard her in Yujie Hub

121
00:11:35,701 --> 00:11:39,862
to try to injure her and buy you time.

122
00:11:42,621 --> 00:11:45,661
I mean no disrespect.

123
00:11:45,661 --> 00:11:50,082
But your attacks wouldn't leave a scratch on her.

124
00:11:50,082 --> 00:11:52,302
Not necessarily.

125
00:11:52,302 --> 00:11:58,041
If we hit the weakest spot on her scale, it could produce miracles.

126
00:12:02,641 --> 00:12:05,322
So you've planned out everything.

127
00:12:05,322 --> 00:12:10,021
If I can't persuade the Righteous Martial Alliance, none of this matters then.

128
00:12:11,741 --> 00:12:16,882
There have been occurrences of petrification all over the land.

129
00:12:16,882 --> 00:12:19,562
According to Zhu Yu's route,

130
00:12:19,562 --> 00:12:24,840
I speculate that her next destination is Jing'an.

131
00:12:28,621 --> 00:12:30,362
Why didn't you say so sooner?

132
00:12:35,702 --> 00:12:37,781
I understand now.

133
00:12:37,781 --> 00:12:39,582
You're only saying it now

134
00:12:39,582 --> 00:12:42,661
because you want the Righteous Martial Alliance to get a taste of Zhu Yu's power

135
00:12:42,661 --> 00:12:45,281
and force them to cooperate with you.

136
00:12:45,281 --> 00:12:49,042
Is it really that hard to tell people to leave the city and seek refuge?

137
00:12:49,042 --> 00:12:51,282
Would it cost you your lives?

138
00:13:06,541 --> 00:13:08,642
How strange.

139
00:13:08,642 --> 00:13:15,282
I always feel that we should be close to him.

140
00:13:15,282 --> 00:13:17,582
Is it an illusion?

141
00:13:24,141 --> 00:13:25,910
It must be.

142
00:13:26,582 --> 00:13:29,582
Qi. Qi?

143
00:13:30,441 --> 00:13:32,182
Hey, Jinzhao, what is it?

144
00:13:32,182 --> 00:13:35,022
We're setting off for Jing'an soon. I'll explain it later.

145
00:13:35,022 --> 00:13:37,962
Hurry and call Xian Qing and the others. Quick.

146
00:13:45,261 --> 00:13:49,201
For the Hengdao Sect, life is something that can be measured.

147
00:13:49,201 --> 00:13:50,781
The lives of millions of people

148
00:13:50,781 --> 00:13:54,062
are insignificant compared to the lives of all in the Six Realms.

149
00:13:54,062 --> 00:13:57,641
Let alone it's just the lives of the civilians in Jing'an City.

150
00:13:57,641 --> 00:14:00,202
Hengdao Sect is watching the world from above.

151
00:14:00,202 --> 00:14:02,490
They must feel like gods.

152
00:14:03,201 --> 00:14:06,882
The Hengdao Sect doesn't take people seriously at all.

153
00:14:06,882 --> 00:14:11,801
Not just the Hengdao Sect, Zhu Yu doesn't either.

154
00:14:12,982 --> 00:14:14,401
Exactly.

155
00:14:16,222 --> 00:14:18,002
No one should be given up.

156
00:14:18,002 --> 00:14:21,102
Every life deserves respect.

157
00:14:21,102 --> 00:14:22,381
Qi is right.

158
00:14:22,381 --> 00:14:27,202
Even the smallest life is unique and has the right to live.

159
00:14:28,541 --> 00:14:29,861
Once we arrive in Jing'an,

160
00:14:29,861 --> 00:14:32,141
we must ask the Righteous Martial Alliance to convince the residents

161
00:14:32,141 --> 00:14:34,181
to flee as far away as possible.

162
00:14:35,141 --> 00:14:41,522
Miss Ming, why don't you and Qi see how far Jing'an is from here?

163
00:14:55,781 --> 00:14:57,661
You deliberately sent them away.

164
00:14:57,661 --> 00:15:00,482
Is there something you wanted to discuss with me?

165
00:15:00,482 --> 00:15:06,182
I suspect that Ying Xuwei kept the method to undo the bindings from me.

166
00:15:06,182 --> 00:15:08,202
Why would he?

167
00:15:08,202 --> 00:15:11,261
They say opening Rehai would free Mist Soul.

168
00:15:11,261 --> 00:15:16,742
But on that day, Zhu Yu will lead the Yu clan to Earth,

169
00:15:16,742 --> 00:15:19,021
