170
00:15:19,021 --> 00:15:23,982
How can we be sure Mist Soul will be freed just by absorbing the power of Rehai?

171
00:15:26,661 --> 00:15:31,001
Perhaps he kept it from you because he thought you couldn't accept it.

172
00:15:31,001 --> 00:15:33,282
So he avoided talking about it.

173
00:15:35,702 --> 00:15:38,423
There's only one thing I can't accept.

174
00:15:38,423 --> 00:15:40,462
That is harm to those I care about.

175
00:15:42,021 --> 00:15:44,642
Quick, look! There's dark clouds over there!

176
00:15:49,362 --> 00:15:51,322
It's Zhu Yu.

177
00:15:54,822 --> 00:15:58,082
There's no time. We must hurry down there.

178
