Careful.

180
00:16:29,062 --> 00:16:30,302
Are you okay?

181
00:16:30,302 --> 00:16:31,881
Over here.

182
00:16:36,261 --> 00:16:38,081
Miss Ming!

183
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:42,501
- What's wrong? 
 - His leg.

184
00:16:42,501 --> 00:16:44,921
Let me do it.

185
00:16:44,921 --> 00:16:46,901
It's fine.

186
00:16:47,942 --> 00:16:49,741
Try to endure it.

187
00:17:24,982 --> 00:17:26,742
- Here. 
 - Here. Have some water.

188
00:17:26,742 --> 00:17:28,562
Have some water.

189
00:17:32,862 --> 00:17:34,582
Thank you.

190
00:17:38,261 --> 00:17:41,721
You haven't rested in a long time. Go rest.

191
00:17:41,721 --> 00:17:43,781
I'm fine.

192
00:17:45,061 --> 00:17:49,722
Brother Yue and Miss Yue are having it harder in Jing'an.

193
00:18:08,101 --> 00:18:10,602
Jinzhao, I can absorb the Qiyuan Orb.

194
00:18:10,602 --> 00:18:12,522
I want to save them.

195
00:18:14,222 --> 00:18:17,901
I'll help you. Together.

