00:19:03,125 --> 00:19:06,425
♫  The world is in turmoil, but it doesn't matter  ♫

208
00:19:06,425 --> 00:19:13,422
♫  You're fighting against the world alongside me  ♫

209
00:19:13,422 --> 00:19:16,933
♫  Writing legends with your sword ♫ 

