00:19:16,933 --> 00:19:19,890
♫  You and I, side by side  ♫

211
00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:24,050
♫  Unafraid of the trials of love and hate  ♫

212
00:19:24,050 --> 00:19:27,729
♫  This destined path is full of turbulence,  ♫

213
00:19:27,729 --> 00:19:30,282
♫  But it doesn't matter, watch me forge ahead  ♫

214
00:19:30,282 --> 00:19:36,227
♫  I wander around, carefree  ♫

