00:19:38,382 --> 00:19:40,182
Your medicine.

216
00:20:11,541 --> 00:20:14,401
Did Jinzhao and Young Yue succeed?

217
00:20:15,501 --> 00:20:17,982
Let's take the people back to Jing'an first,

218
00:20:17,982 --> 00:20:21,061
and then find Young Master Yue and Miss Yue.

