00:20:41,182 --> 00:20:45,062
- Qi. 
 - Young Yue, are you okay?

221
00:20:47,021 --> 00:20:50,222
Jinzhao, I'll stay here to assess the situation.

222
00:20:50,222 --> 00:20:52,624
You all go to the Righteous Martial Alliance.

223
00:20:55,462 --> 00:20:57,081
Okay.

224
00:20:58,301 --> 00:21:01,681
Miss Yue, let's go together.

