00:21:15,322 --> 00:21:16,541
What is it?

228
00:21:16,541 --> 00:21:21,222
Quite a few members of the alliance are also wearing Qiyuan Orbs.

229
00:21:34,261 --> 00:21:35,702
Lingyun!

230
00:21:38,840 --> 00:21:41,622
- Leader. 
 - Leader Zuo.

231
00:21:41,622 --> 00:21:43,242
Leader Zuo.

232
00:21:44,821 --> 00:21:48,601
Hero Yue, Jing'an City has suffered a great calamity.

233
00:21:48,601 --> 00:21:51,401
I must deal with it first.

