00:21:51,401 --> 00:21:53,382
You all can do as you wish.

235
00:21:53,382 --> 00:21:55,062
Come.

236
00:21:57,341 --> 00:21:59,240
Let's go to Mechanic Skill Hall.

237
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,880
Okay.

238
00:22:03,422 --> 00:22:06,602
Why are there victims of the Qiyuan Orbs in the alliance?

239
00:22:06,602 --> 00:22:08,901
- Find out. 
 - Yes.

240
00:22:11,821 --> 00:22:13,382
In more than two hundred years,

241
00:22:13,382 --> 00:22:15,842
Rehai, which should've moved in a defined trajectory,

242
00:22:15,842 --> 00:22:18,061
was bound to my family by Maiming.

243
00:22:18,061 --> 00:22:20,001
Now, the Bloodbinding has been lifted.

244
00:22:20,001 --> 00:22:22,621
Naturally, it has returned to its course.

245
00:22:27,021 --> 00:22:30,042
This is a map of the Luo family. Look.

246
00:22:32,982 --> 00:22:36,641
If we connect these places...

247
00:22:37,501 --> 00:22:40,142
This is the moving trajectory of Rehai.

248
00:22:41,101 --> 00:22:43,142
Rehai is the force of life.

249
00:22:43,142 --> 00:22:47,541
Wherever it's been, an oasis will form over a long period.

250
00:22:47,541 --> 00:22:49,702
Even today, in places like Buried Wind Plains,

251
00:22:49,702 --> 00:22:52,681
one can still see traces of its former lushness.

252
00:22:53,662 --> 00:22:55,581
The Yu Clan lived underwater.

253
00:22:55,581 --> 00:22:57,781
They aren't suited to move well in arid places.

254
00:22:57,781 --> 00:23:01,562
Zhu Yu certainly won't try to absorb Rehai in the desert.

255
00:23:01,562 --> 00:23:05,222
A few days ago, Rehai began to move from my family's domain.

256
00:23:05,222 --> 00:23:08,101
